# Trained model weights are stored here.
# They are NOT committed to git due to file size.
#
# Download pre-trained weights:
#   python scripts/download_weights.py
#
# Or train from scratch:
#   python backend/notebooks/train_pneumonia_yolov8.py
#
# Expected files:
#   yolov8_pneumonia.pt        - YOLOv8 weights (Ultralytics format)
#   yolov8_pneumonia.pkl       - Serialised sklearn pipeline (preprocessing)
#   label_encoder.pkl          - Severity label encoder
